videos.headline: Hilinski drops a dime to Edwards for Gamecocks TD
videos.description: Ryan Hilinski airs it out to WR Bryan Edwards, who drags two Bulldog defenders into the end zone with him for a touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-play (Hilinski drops a dime to Edwards for Gamecocks TD) 2019/10/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Swift pounds his way through defenders for TD
videos.description: D'Andre Swift shows off his strength as he powers his way over the goal line for a touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-play (Swift pounds his way through defenders for TD) 2019/10/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Fromm's first interception turns into pick-six
videos.description: Jake Fromm slings one under pressure to the sideline, where South Carolina's Israel Mukuamu snags it for a pick-six before the half.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Fromm’s first interception turns into pick-six) 2019/10/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Blankenship's field goal deflected before half
videos.description: Rodrigo Blankenship's leg was no match for the Gamecocks defensive line as his 53-yard field goal attempt was deflected right before half time.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Blankenship's field goal deflected before half) 2019/10/12

videos.headline: South Carolina's Mukuamu picks off Fromm again
videos.description: South Carolina's Israel Mukuamu has Jake Fromm's number as he dives for his second interception off a miss-thrown ball.

videos.headline: Robertson barely stays in bounds to tie game late
videos.description: Georgia WR Demetris Robertson hauls in a perfect pass from Jake Fromm and stays in bounds to tie the game at 17-17 vs. South Carolina.

videos.headline: Georgia's Fromm throws INT OT
videos.description: South Carolina's Israel Mukuamu pulls off the hat trick, intercepting Jack Fromm for a third time, this time in overtime.

videos.headline: Hilinski stunned as South Carolina misses game-winning field goal attempt
videos.description: Parker White sends game-winning field goal attempt wide ride in overtime, leaving South Carolina QB Ryan Hilinski stunned.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Hilinski stunned as South Carolina misses game-winning field goal attempt) 2019/10/12

videos.headline: Georgia loses as Blankenship misses FG in 2OT
videos.description: Rodrigo Blankenship barely misses the uprights in double overtime and the Gamecocks pull off the upset win against the Bulldogs.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Georgia loses as Blankenship misses FG in double overtime) 2019/10/12

videos.headline: Muschamp hurts for Blankenship after missed kick
videos.description: South Carolina head coach Will Muschamp says he feels for Georgia K Rodrigo Blankenship and describes what this win means for the Gamecocks.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Interview (Muschamp hurts for Blankenship after missed kick) 2019/10/12
